# Scale Up

## Introduction

In this task, we aim to scale up our web infrastructure by introducing additional components and splitting existing ones to improve performance and reliability.

## Requirements

- **1 Server:**
  - We will add one server to accommodate the increased load and distribute the workload effectively.

- **1 Load-Balancer (HAProxy) Configured as Cluster with Another One:**
  - HAProxy will be configured as a cluster with another instance to provide high availability and distribute incoming traffic across multiple servers.

- **Split Components:**
  - The components, including the web server, application server, and database, will be split onto their own individual servers. This separation enhances scalability, fault isolation, and resource management.

