## Specifics

- **Additional Elements Rationale:**
  - Adding another server and load-balancer enhances scalability and fault tolerance, ensuring the infrastructure can handle increased traffic and recover from failures.
  
- **Load-Balancer Configuration:**
  - HAProxy will be configured as a cluster with another instance to provide redundancy and distribute traffic evenly across servers, improving performance and reliability.
  
- **Splitting Components:**
  - Splitting components onto separate servers allows for better resource allocation, isolation of faults, and easier management and scaling of individual components.

## Conclusion

By implementing the above requirements and specifics, we aim to enhance the scalability, reliability, and performance of our web infrastructure to meet the demands of increased traffic and ensure seamless operation.
